                   User Interface    Pseucode 
                   
                   
           Goal 
            
            User start the game by clicking on a hand . he plays the game until a score of 5 from user or computer
            
            
        Pseudo code 
        
        create a  user screen 
         create 3 buttons 
         in the user screen : separe it to three parts 
                 -user play ground  left 
                 computer playGround right
                 - computer scores and user scores in the middle
                 - at the end of the game output the result on the full screen 
         Every button contain the img of the user hand centered
